# GitHub Actions repository secrets. Copy to .env.gh.secrets and fill in values, then run:
#   ./scripts/setup-repo.sh
# Or set in GitHub: Settings → Secrets and variables → Actions (or: gh secret set NAME, then paste value).
#
# Deploy: use Coolify Auto Deploy on main + branch protection (no secrets). Optional webhook trigger only if you disable Auto Deploy:
# COOLIFY_WEBHOOK=...
# COOLIFY_TOKEN=...
#
# Optional: production smoke workflow (scripts/smoke-prod.sh, scheduled + manual):
# INFERENCIA_SMOKE_BASE_URL=https://llm.yourdomain.com
# INFERENCIA_E2E_API_KEY=sk-your-api-key
#
# Optional: CI connectivity check (app must reach backend from GitHub runners):
# INFERENCIA_CI_BACKEND_URL=http://your-backend:11973
# INFERENCIA_CI_API_KEYS=sk-test-key
